data.description: Price Reduced. Come and see this ready to move in house with master on the main level. This immaculate well cared for home is hard to find and centrally located near shopping, schools and easy freeway access.  Beautiful, light and open concept.  An inviting kitchen with stainless steel appliances, double ovens and plenty of cabinet space - a chef's delight. The ideal main floor living includes the kitchen; laundry room;  a well designed attached 18x13 sun room; and the master bedroom and bathroom suite.  The upper level includes 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom and a loft area perfect for an office or a den. Neutral colors, plantation shutters, high quality carpet, storage space, updated plumbing and electrical fixtures throughout.  This home is waiting for someone like you to enjoy it for years to come. This home is perfect for someone that doesn't like to take care of allot of yard.
